profile_positions.description:
Analyse current market condition in relevant fields, forecast future industry performance and make procurement recommendations;
Analyse production chains, supply and demand trends to support the supplier evaluation and negotiation process;
Translate & analyse internal customer requirements, develop business cases and monitor progress;
Provide analytical support for category strategy development and communicate them clearly to stakeholders;
Help to establish and adhere to the purchasing guidelines based on the strategies and goals created;Managed the execution of purchase orders
Organize, plan and coordinate procurement activities that support efficient operations;
Report key findings to senior management.
